<h2 id="_3-最终结论-散射角" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-最终结论-散射角"><span>3. 最终结论：散射角 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span></span></span></span></a></h2>
<p>由于中心力场中轨道关于近地点（<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r_{\min}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3175em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mop mtight"><span class="mtight">m</span><span class="mtight">i</span><span class="mtight">n</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>）对称：</p>
<ul>
<li>入射渐近线与近地点连线夹角为 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ψ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\psi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ψ</span></span></span></span>。</li>
<li>出射渐近线与近地点连线夹角也为 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ψ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\psi</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ψ</span></span></span></span>。</li>
<li>入射与出射的总夹角（即<strong>散射角</strong> <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span></span></span>）为：</li>
</ul>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>ψ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta = |\pi - 2\psi|

</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">π</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ψ</span><span class="mord">∣</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>联立积分式，即得两体散射问题的通解公式：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">∣</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></msubsup><mfrac><mi>s</mi><mrow><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msqrt><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mi>E</mi></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mfrac><mi>d</mi><mi>r</mi><mo fence="true">∣</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta = \left| \pi - 2 \int_{r_{\min}}^{\infty} \frac{s}{r^2 \sqrt{1 - \frac{V(r)}{E} - \frac{s^2}{r^2}}} dr \right|

